{
  "doc_id": "9345",
  "text": "Numerous studies of eukaryotes revealed that mitochondrion morphology is complicated and plastic [CITATION_1] Bereiter-Hahn & Voth, 1994; [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . According to the literature data, long mitochondria with tubular cristae localized in the peripheral cytoplasm layer are characteristic of diatoms (Round et al., 1990, p. 60) . Comparative studies of mitochondrion structure have not been performed before.",
